name: Kidou Senshi Gundam: Gihren no Yabou: Axis no Kyoui V
overview: Kidou Senshi Gundam: Gihren no Yabou - Axis no Kyoui V is a Strategy game, developed by Bec and published by Bandai Namco Games, which was released in Japan in 2009. Is an expanded version of Kidou Senshi Gundam: Gihren no Yabou - Axis no Kyoui.
